{
  "title": "ISic003472. Fragment of a decree(?)",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GRB3IPD5\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GRB3IPD5</a></div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΕΤΙΑΙΤΕΙΔΕΚΥ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΝΤΩΓΓΝΗ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΝΤΩΜΠΑ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]Κ<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.</span>ΑΣΤΟΣ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΜΙΥΠΟΚΑΚ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΙΣΟΡΟΦΑΝΕΔ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al7-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΚΛΕΠΤΟΣΑΝΕ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al8-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">8</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΑΣ <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.)</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GRB3IPD5\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GRB3IPD5</a></div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΕΤΙΑΙΤΕΙΔΕΚΥ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΝΤΩΓΓΝΗ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΝΤΩΜΠΑ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]Κ<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">·</span>ΑΣΤΟΣ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΜΙΥΠΟΚΑΚ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΙΣΟΡΟΦΑΝΕΔ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al7-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΚΛΕΠΤΟΣΑΝΕ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al8-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">8</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΑΣ&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of Manganaro 1999</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Manganaro suggests this is a decree of Akrai, published in villages in the city's territory. He speculates that the text makes reference to a theft, and perhaps involving a sacred building or sanctuary (line 6: ε]ἰς ὀροφὰν ΕΔ[--; and line 7: ἐ]κλέπτοσαν Ε[--). The text is notable as a rare example of an early Hellenistic document.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 49.1268 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> Manganaro 1999 55-57 no.B fig.126 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001813\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001813</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"><p>Alpha with wide form and straight bar; Epsilon with three equal horizontal bars; Nu of an open and right-ward angled form; sigma four bar and widely angled open; pi with shorter right hasta.</p> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
